<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="pack-v">pack <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /pæk/    美 /pæk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(把…) 打包；(把…) 装进 (箱子等) ：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t forget to pack your toothbrush! 
别忘了把牙刷放到箱子里去!</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I haven’t packed yet. 
我还没收拾行李呢。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They hurriedly <strong>packed their things / belongings</strong> into the suitcase.
他们匆忙地把东西装进了行李箱。</p><footer>2009 江西改</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>塞满；挤满：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>More than two thousand students packed the hall. 
两千多名学生把礼堂挤得满满的。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We all <strong>packed into</strong> one car.
我们都挤进了一辆车里。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The bus was <strong>packed with</strong> people. 
公共汽车上挤满了人。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="pack-up">pack up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>把…打包；收拾 (行李)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Once a friend and I packed up some peanut butter and sandwiches for an outing. 
有一次，我和一个朋友包好一些花生酱和三明治去郊游。</p><footer>2009 浙江</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>We were first greeted with the barking by a pack <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ dogs, seven to be exact.  （2019 全国）  </li>
<li>The workers <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (把…打包) the glasses and marked on each box “This Side Up”.  （2010 全国改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. of  2. packed  </p></div>